<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<div data-role="header" data-position="fixed" data-backbtn="false">
  <h1><%= "Goal Buster" %></h1>
</div>

<div class="info-txt" data-role="content">
  In joining, you'll be given a unique team by random from a pot of premiership teams.
  <p>
    The person with the team that is first to score exactly 11 goals from a series of fixtures is the winner.
  <p>
    Teams left in the pot: <%= @available_choices_count %>
</div>
<p>
  <%= form_for(@bet) do |bet| %>
    <div align="center">
      <%= bet.submit 'Join', class: 'btn btn-large btn-primary', disabled: !@round.open? %>
    </div>
<% end %>
<p>
  <% unless @round.open? %>
    <div class="info-txt-clear" align="center">
      Available from <%= @round.open_at.in_time_zone('London').strftime('%e %B %l%P') %>
    </div>
<% end %>

<%= render 'common/footer' %>
</html>
